<div class="landing">
  <div class="landing-hero">
    <h1 class="landing-title">ThesisTrack</h1>
    <p class="landing-tagline">Final Year Project Supervision Platform</p>
    <p class="landing-desc">Manage your final year project, stay in touch with your supervisor, track tasks and feedback—all in one place.</p>
    <div class="landing-actions">
      <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
      <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-secondary btn-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-features">
    <div class="landing-feature card">
      <h3>For Students</h3>
      <p>Create your project, manage tasks and deadlines, upload documents with version history, and receive structured feedback from your supervisor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="landing-feature card">
      <h3>For Supervisors</h3>
      <p>Overview of all your supervisees, track project progress, schedule meetings, exchange messages, and give feedback linked to document versions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="landing-how-to-use" id="how-to-use" aria-labelledby="how-to-use-title">
    <h2 class="landing-how-to-use-title" id="how-to-use-title">How to use</h2>
    <p class="landing-how-to-use-lead">Get started with ThesisTrack in a few steps.</p>
    <div class="landing-how-to-use-grid">
      <div class="landing-how-to-use-block card">
        <h3>Students</h3>
        <ol class="landing-how-to-use-steps">
          <li>Sign up and add your supervisor’s email when prompted.</li>
          <li>Create your project with a title and description from your dashboard.</li>
          <li>Use the project tabs to manage tasks, meetings, messages, and documents.</li>
          <li>Upload documents and request feedback; your supervisor can comment on specific sections.</li>
          <li>Mark phases complete as you progress; keep an eye on deadlines and messages.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-how-to-use-block card">
        <h3>Supervisors</h3>
        <ol class="landing-how-to-use-steps">
          <li>Sign up as a supervisor; students can then select you when they register.</li>
          <li>Use the dashboard to see all your supervisees and risk flags.</li>
          <li>Open each project to manage tasks, schedule meetings, and send messages.</li>
          <li>Give feedback on documents and acknowledge messages to keep communication clear.</li>
          <li>Use the Risk dashboard and activity flags to prioritise follow-ups.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
